section.section:
"Control share acquisition" does not include the acquisition of shares:
Before November 4, 1988;
Under a contract made before November 4, 1988;
Under the laws of descent and distribution;
Under the satisfaction of a pledge or other security interest created in good faith and not for the purpose of circumventing this subtitle;
Under a merger, consolidation, or share exchange effected under Subtitle 1 of this title if the corporation is a party to the merger, consolidation, or share exchange; or
Within one-tenth or more but less than one-fifth of all voting power of outstanding shares of stock of the corporation before June 1, 2000.
